---
title: Calorie Smart Greek-Inspired Tofu with Lemony Roasted Potatoes and Feta Snap Peas
description: All the familiar flavours of Greek cuisine are packed into this better-for-you dinner! Garlicky tofu, lemony roasted potatoes and feta snap peas round out this weeknight winner, which is finished with a dollop of yogurt sauce.

Calorie Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's kilocalorie amount
